<div class="about-hero">
  <div class="container">
    <h1>About ACW</h1>
    <p>
      Assistive Commons Watch monitors the health of open-source assistive technology projects —
      tracking activity, replicability, and community engagement so builders can
      find projects worth contributing to and users can find tools worth relying on.
    </p>
  </div>
</div>

